                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Understand</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">We learn your standards, students, and constraints. No two schools are the same.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-6">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">2</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Design</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Using AI tools and PBL expertise, we craft curriculum that's rigorous and engaging.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-6">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">3</div>
                    <div>
