            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12">What you get</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-6 max-w-3xl">
                <li class="flex gap-4">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-lg font-bold text-blue-600">âœ“</span>
                    <div>
