                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-4">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-lg font-bold text-blue-600">âœ“</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Student-facing materials</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Project briefs, handouts, and digital resources</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-4">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 text-lg font-bold text-blue-600">âœ“</span>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Assessment tools</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Rubrics, reflection prompts, and portfolio guides</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-4">
