            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
                <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=Curriculum Services Inquiry" class="btn btn-primary text-white rounded-lg px-6 py-3 no-underline font-medium min-h-[48px] active:scale-95">
